The following use-cases are integrated in this activity diagram:
- Activate bonus-option for transcripts or bonus-learning with specific cards (lecturer)
- Choose format fitting to content of card set (lecturer)
- Link transcript to lecture to earn bonus points (student)
- Learn with card sets and repetitories based on the method of Leitner or Woźniak paired with the Pomodoro-technique (student)
